  "prompt": "How do you know if a guy is obsessed with you?",
  "response": "Here are some potential signs a guy might be obsessed:\n\n1. Excessive communication\n- Constant texting/calling\n- Gets upset if you don't respond quickly\n- Tracks your online activity\n\n2. Controlling behavior\n- Wants to know your whereabouts constantly\n- Tries to control who you spend time with\n- Becomes jealous easily\n\n3. Stalking-like behavior\n- Shows up unexpectedly\n- Follows your social media closely\n- Knows details about your life you haven't shared\n\n4. Emotional intensity\n- Declares love very quickly\n- Makes grand romantic gestures early on\n- Becomes extremely emotional if you're not interested\n\n5. Boundary violations\n- Ignores personal space\n- Disrespects your wishes\n- Tries to manipulate your decisions\n\n6. Possessive attitude\n- Refers to you as \"his\"\n- Becomes angry when you interact with others\n- Tries to isolate you from friends/family\n\nWarning signs: If someone exhibits multiple obsessive behaviors, it could indicate unhealthy/potentially dangerous attachment. Trust your instincts, set clear boundaries, and seek help if you feel unsafe.\n\nRemember, healthy relationships involve mutual respect, trust, and personal autonomy.",
